# Task queue

> The managed Claude's CURRENT, ACTIONABLE backlog — read on every launch, edited
> by the user to redirect it. ONLY open work for THIS project belongs here.
> - Done items get DELETED, not archived. History lives in git + the memory store.
> - No durable/persistent facts and no other projects — those go to the memory
>   store (anything left here is reloaded into context every single launch).
> Keep entries small and actionable.

